#: src/faq.ui:8 src/faq.ui:32
msgid "FAQ & Common Issues"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:45
msgid "What is this app?"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:56
msgid ""
"Nyarch Updater is a utility application designed to help you keep your "
"system up to date! It allows package updates, flatpak updates, and most "
"importantly, Nyarch release updates."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:74
msgid ""
"Clicking buttons such as \"execute command\" or \"show commands\" does "
"nothing"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:85
msgid ""
"This is a known issue that we are trying to fix. In the meantime, restarting "
"the app should make it work. I would say: restart it until it works, and "
"until we fix it."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:103
msgid "Executing a command did nothing"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:114
msgid ""
"Something went wrong here. Click \"show command\" and execute it yourself. "
"If it persists, please report it in the Discord or the Github."
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:132
msgid ""
"The application keeps asking me to update my release even though I did all "
"the steps"
msgstr ""

#: src/faq.ui:143
msgid ""
"Something went wrong here, again. Don't worry, it's probably not your fault! "
"Check if you didn't skip the \"update version file\" step! If you didn't and "
"it still does not work, copy the command shown with \"Show Command\", and "
"run it after finishing the steps on your preferred terminal emulator. Then "
"restart updater to see the changes!"
msgstr ""

